<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/54b7cd9fc4bbf8d4a28aa3bb2df3b1852.png"></span><span>Undying Will II</span></dt><dd><div>Increases Audric's attack rate by 2% every time<br>he uses a skill (up to 10%) and grants him a skill<br>reservoir with three levels. This skill reservoir is<br>filled when standard attacks, force strikes, and<br>dash attacks connect with enemies.<br><br>Also, grants Audric a defense amp with a<br>maximum team amp level of three every two<br>times he uses a skill. After this amp is granted,<br>this ability will not grant it again for 30 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/5d2fb975c50c8d82b92b435c6ba55b762.png"></span><span>Interdimensional Blessing II</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to poison<br>and curses by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/85285afa2a77c2880c1c006d8d0d214c2.png"></span><span>Gauge Accelerator +35%</span></dt><dd><div>Speeds the rate the mode gauge decreases by 35%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities and represent the adventurers at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Some skills have different effects when used as a shared skill.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. Alberian Battle Royale skins for the adventurers featured in this summon showcase are on sale and cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1650002400,update_time1648549302